00:04:50.969 --> 00:04:52.170
when they flag issues.

00:04:53.070 --> 00:04:55.318
This talk is also
for designers, developers,

00:04:55.319 --> 00:04:57.960
and content creators
who are working in WordPress,

00:04:58.230 --> 00:05:01.109
who may have identified issues
on the sites that they're working

00:05:01.110 --> 00:05:03.269
on and need to fix those issues.

00:05:04.320 --> 00:05:08.879
