00:50:42.500 --> 00:50:44.000
Specifically to WordPress,

00:50:44.360 --> 00:50:46.670
I think if you're using
a map on a WordPress,

00:50:47.359 --> 00:50:48.409
you're probably using

00:50:49.069 --> 00:50:52.699
some sort of plugin or you're embedding
something from another site,

00:50:53.179 --> 00:50:54.740
and so in that case,

00:50:54.859 --> 00:50:57.229
I would just want
to do as much testing as possible

00:50:57.230 --> 00:51:02.259
on whatever it is you're bringing in
and make sure that that is accessible,

00:51:02.439 --> 00:51:05.558
and in that case, you're going to have
to work with whatever plugin you're using

00:51:05.559 --> 00:51:08.261
or whatever other site
you're embedding into.

00:51:09.430 --> 00:51:11.773
I think that's the most I can say
on that and this time.

